posts.description: Martin O’Malley talks Donald Trump, Fascism with Jorge Ramos | Fusion
posts.extended: Martin O’Malley says he’s not going to stop punching back against the “racist language” of Donald Trump—in part because he says the Republican’s rhetoric is the kind that has historically led to fascism.
